Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:58.74,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}Shaded by the trees, calling out to the wind, I'm lying face-down crying
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:08.51,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}I saw a version of myself I didn't even recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:17.86,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}On this guitar I'm playing the melody of someone who's passed on
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:27.00,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}A star falls in the grief of someone who'll never be seen again
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:35.83,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}Please don't go, no matter how much you scream,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:46.32,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}All it will do is quietly stir these orange petals
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:54.60,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}Saved on my soft brow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:18:00.45,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}I send the memories in my palm far away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:12.13,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}An eternal farewell as I keep strumming
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:31.67,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}The heart of a child clinging to a gentle hand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:40.43,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}The blazing wheels cast it off and continue on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:49.14,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}On this guitar I'm playing the grief of someone who's passed on
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:56.94,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}The strings in my heart being plucked at violently
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:19:05.58,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}In the pure white unstained by sorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:15.35,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}The orange petals stirred in a summer shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:22.94,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}Even if my soft brow is lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:31.34,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}I'll cross over the far off, red-stained sand
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:39.99,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1900}The rhythm of farewell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:54.59,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}Branded into my memories, on the ever-turning earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:20:02.66,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}There is something sprouting in remembrance
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:45.86,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}Sending off the dawn's carriage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:55.70,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}Those orange petals are stirring somewhere even now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:21:03.32,Internal Song,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300}The peaceful daybreak I once saw
