Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.03,0:22:20.71,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fs40\3c&H303030&\4c&H606060&\1c&HD1FFCE&}umaku yukanai modokashisa ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:16.03,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}Frustrated because
