Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:25.74,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,I hugged my knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:35.91,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,Repressing my anger, the tears fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:40.26,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,and I cried until dawn broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:46.82,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm certain that you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:52.10,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can turn back right now but,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:57.91,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still holding on to my foolish pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:00.45,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up because
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:03.49,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've started walking my own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.50,0:23:08.38,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need one more chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:13.82,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold all my feelings in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:17.90,GSEnglish-Ending2,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my dreams come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:25.74,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kakaekonda hiza kozou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:35.91,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kuyashisa wo koraete namida ni furuete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:40.26,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}naita yoru ga akeru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:46.82,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sou tashika ni kimi no iu toori da yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.85,0:22:52.10,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ima nara hikikaeseru keredomo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:57.91,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}tsumaranai iji wo haritsuduketeru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.98,0:23:00.45,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}arukihajimeta ijou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:03.49,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}akiramenai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.50,0:23:08.38,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mou ichido kono te ni chansu wo...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:13.82,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}subete kono mune no naka ni shimatte okou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:17.90,GSKaraoke-Ending2-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}yume ga kanau made.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:12.19,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find the words,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:15.53,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,so I touched your shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.89,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,Without saying a word,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:22.04,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,you coldly took my hand away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:25.34,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of a little misunderstanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:28.68,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,our young love was shattering
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:35.78,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see your face so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:38.69,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when your dreams are gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:42.92,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't throw away your smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:48.90,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is still shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.70,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,We swore that one day we'd
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:57.01,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,build the future with our own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:59.95,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.61,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:07.71,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we look away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.05,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,with pained eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:15.43,GSEnglish-Opening3,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe we'll be able to meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:12.19,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,kotoba mitsukerarezu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:15.53,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,omowazu fureta katasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:18.89,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi wa nanni mo iwazu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:22.04,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,tsumetaku furihodoku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:25.34,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,Honno sasaina gokai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:28.68,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,osanai ai wa kuzureteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.75,0:01:35.78,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,sonna kanashii kao wa mitakunai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:38.69,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,Yume sae nakushitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:42.92,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,sono hohoemi dake sutenaide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:48.90,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono mune kagayaiteite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:53.70,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuka chikau bokura
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:57.01,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,kono te de kizuku mirai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.08,0:01:59.95,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanarazu kono basho de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.61,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi ga doko ni itatte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:07.71,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,Dakedo ima wa futari setsunaku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.05,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,sorashita hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.13,0:02:15.43,GSKaraoke-Opening3-Romanji,,0000,0000,0000,,deaeru koto wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:05.59,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,To jednoducho nemôže byť pravda, že je MIA.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:10.10,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,To jednoducho nie je pravda. tak... tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:15.80,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja. ..som ho zabil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:20.31,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Už nebol nepriateľom! Bol na mojej strane!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.94,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemal som inú možnosť, ako ho zabiť, nie?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:25.55,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Je zrejme mŕtvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.31,0:00:27.28,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz, ma nechaj tak!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:32.22,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira? Mŕtvy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.22,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to amulet z Haumea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:40.56,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Máš sklon sa dostať do tažkostí\NBude ťa chrániť.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:44.17,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Aj keď som zabil Kiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:46.87,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem aby bol ktokolvek mŕtvy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:53.67,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobré ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:29.84,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Spríevodný system online na x-alpha-alpha\NKanál Omega-3.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:31.81,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}sekvencia ide.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:33.98,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Správa z kontrolného úradu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:37.54,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,System online na omega 3.\NSekvencia ide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.85,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Potom, čo ste potvrdili signál,\NPráporčík, prepnite na auto-navigáciu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:44.19,Normal,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvyšok nechajte na nich.
